{"tid":1394244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【新聞】美國上訴法庭維持原判 中國三家銀行協助北朝洗錢","createTime":"2019-08-01T10:50:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T06:51:54.000Z","uid":45910,"like":117,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"04c7382741a23336459fc317681b1a3378e57394","tid":1394244,"uid":45910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:50:59.000Z","msg":"【新聞】美國上訴法庭維持原判 中國三家銀行協助北朝洗錢<br />\n <br />\n據路透社7月31日訊，今年5月，交通銀行、招商銀行和上海浦東發展銀行因涉嫌通過香港明正國際貿易公司協助朝鮮對外貿易銀行進行洗錢（至少1億美元），並拒絕履行地區法庭提交相關交易文件的傳票，繼而被判藐視法庭。上訴法庭於本週二庭審中維持原判，即三家銀行將繼續繳納每日5萬美元的罰金。<br />\n <br />\n美國愛國者法案授權首席檢察官或財政部長可停止違反法院傳票要求的金融機構進行美元項下交易。三家銀行表示不能遵守傳票要求是因為來自中共的命令。它們可選擇再次申請上訴法庭重審或上訴至最高法院。 【GM29】<br />\n來源：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-trade-china-banks/us-appeals-court-upholds-ruling-against-chinese-banks-in-north-korea-sanctions-probe-idUSKCN1UQ03U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-usa-trade-china-banks%2Fus-appeals-court-upholds-ruling-against-chinese-banks-in-north-korea-sanctions-probe-idUSKCN1UQ03U&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIES9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=06fa0482\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-usa-trade-china-banks%2Fus-appeals-court-upholds-ruling-against-chinese-banks-in-north-korea-sanctions-probe-idUSKCN1UQ03U&h=c796c21f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-trade-china-banks/us-appeals-court-upholds-ruling-against-chinese-banks-in-north-korea-sanctions-probe-idUSKCN1UQ03U</a><br />\n<br />\n用銀通撳爆佢櫃員機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a90527a4daccb2131838d35cfacec4fe84f117ce","tid":1394244,"uid":54181,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:52:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9bc34ea2b2ce2d9b441a98c18442e033cdd0d9ff","tid":1394244,"uid":181088,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":4,